# --- Talkatone 核心分流 ---
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,talkatone.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,tktn.at
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,tktn.be
USER-AGENT,Talkatone*

# --- 关键：强制 UDP 语音流走代理 ---
# 这些是 Talkatone 在美西和美东的核心机房段，必须 no-resolve
IP-CIDR,50.117.27.0/24,no-resolve
IP-CIDR,63.251.124.0/24,no-resolve
IP-CIDR,205.164.56.0/24,no-resolve
IP-CIDR,69.46.241.0/24,no-resolve

# --- 劫持检测绕过 ---
# 很多分流失败是因为 App 探测了以下地址确认你是否在代理环境
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,ip-api.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,ipstack.com
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,stun
